author: By SAM McNEIL Associated Press
title: Masked crowds fill streets and trains in post-lockdown Wuhan
description: WUHAN, China (AP) — After more than two months indoors, Wuhan resident Tong Zhengkun was one of millions of people enjoying a renewed sense of freedom Wednesday when the Chinese city's 76-day coronavirus lockdown was lifted.
